products.Title: Face Oil
products.Unique: This antioxidant-rich, fast-absorbing daily face oil is formulated to nourish skin with the transformative benefits of Mirsalehi Honey, natural actives and freshly cold-pressed botanical oils from the Mirsalehi Bee Garden.
products.Multitasker: Our face oil contains 95.7% cold-pressed botanical oils. What does “cold-pressed” mean? It’s one of the purest forms of extraction that doesn’t use high heat, which can destroy valuable nutrients – vitamins, minerals, antioxidants, fatty acids – found naturally within botanical extracts.

products.Title: Beauty Balm
products.Description: Melts like honey, transforms your skin
products.Unique: A never-before-seen Oil-Balm is the secret to bright, dewy skin. It’s a sustainably-sourced, antioxidant-rich concentrate crafted to nourish skin with the transformative benefits of Mirsalehi Honey, natural actives and freshly cold-pressed botanical oils inspired by the Mirsalehi Bee Garden.\nOur Honey Infused Hair Oil is the key to healthy, shiny and nourished hair. Our first ever product was inspired by the Mirsalehi Bee Garden and contains Mirsalehi Honey, which maintains the hair’s natural moisture balance.
products.Multitasker: At Gisou we believe that healthy skin is beautiful skin. The Honey Infused Beauty Balm is here to tackle problem skin areas to strengthen, protect and hydrate the skin and its barrier while also enhancing your natural beauty by brightening and smoothing.
